</span></p><p class="sc-fIosxK hdNOer pf-39_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cLpAjG dTtSfA pf-41_">Induction and onboarding training in the health and social care sector is a multifaceted process designed to equip new employees with the necessary skills, knowledge, and understanding to perform their roles effectively. It transcends mere orientation, embedding new staff into the culture and ethos of their organisation while aligning them with the sectorâ€™s values and standards.
<br>

