</span></h3><p class="sc-fIosxK hdNOer pf-71_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cLpAjG dTtSfA pf-73_">Induction begins with an introduction to the workplace, including an overview of policies, safety protocols, and team roles. This familiarisation is crucial for integrating employees into their new environment.
