</span></h3><p class="sc-fIosxK hdNOer pf-77_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cLpAjG dTtSfA pf-79_">Mandatory training covers essential areas dictated by regulatory bodies like the CQC. Topics include health and safety, infection control, fire safety, and safeguarding.
