</span></h3><p class="sc-fIosxK hdNOer pf-95_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cLpAjG dTtSfA pf-97_">Communication, teamwork, and empathy training are essential for fostering a compassionate care environment.
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-dFtzxp icSyEj pf-98_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cLpAjG dTtSfA pf-100_">Continuous professional development
